00:11:34.070 --> 00:11:41.220
the page and just deleted the entire article,
ok? And then eventually it gets reverted to

00:11:41.220 --> 00:11:48.149
what it is was back. Over here someone, on
top of deleting the whole thing, said, "Abortion

00:11:48.149 --> 00:11:55.550
is great." And then, "Abortion is good." And
then it got reverted. And what we saw by looking

00:11:55.550 --> 00:12:00.120
at the visualization is when these things
were taking place. So, if I go back to the

00:12:00.120 --> 00:12:06.709
