maybe wonder why so many knees? I dunno. People

00:16:37.449 --> 00:16:43.420
could be down on their knees a lot in the
blues. What about other genres? What about

00:16:43.420 --> 00:16:49.010
heavy metal, for example? Well, here you suddenly
see a greater diversity of body parts for

00:16:49.010 --> 00:16:50.010
sure.

00:16:50.010 --> 00:16:51.010
